 h4.caption【Windows】
 .box start chrome --user-data-dir=D://temp --disable-web-security --disable-site-isolation-trials
 br
 p もしくは
 .box start chrome --user-data-dir=%tmp% --disable-web-security --disable-site-isolation-trials
